---
title: Herby Sausage Risotto with Tomato, Parmesan Cheese, and Zucchini
description: Your family will love how unbelievably creamy this dish is. But you? Well, you’ll love the fact that minimal pots and pans are involved and that our chefs snuck in some veggies underneath all the hearty rice, flavorful Italian sausage, and Parmesan.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/uk-italian-pork-and-tomato-risot-c9bef8bc.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/uk-italian-pork-and-tomato-risot-7a0d4df2.pdf
